nodes.text: The Incom Corporation Z-95 AF4-H was a model of Headhunter. Someone who was familiar with the starfighter line could tell it apart from the Z-95-AF4 Headhunter.
The Z-95 AF4-H was mentioned in Hank Green's short story "A Naturalist on Hoth" in the 2020 anthology From a Certain Point of View: The Empire Strikes Back.
